			title: "Import and Export"
			x: -3.0d
			y: -15.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["AE01000000000015"]
			description: ["Crafting Accelerators reduce the ticks between ingredient dispatch steps inside the Crafting CPU. Each accelerator cuts processing delay by a fixed increment. For short 1-2 step recipes, two accelerators suffice; for deep GTCEu processing trees with many intermediate steps, eight to sixteen accelerators is the practical minimum. Expanded AE adds higher-tier accelerators (x2 through x1M) that multiply dispatch speed further — stack them in the CPU structure for chains that would otherwise take minutes to complete per item."]
			id: "AE01000000000018"
			rewards: [{
				count: 2
