		{
			dependencies: ["AE01000000000009"]
			description: ["P2P Tunnels compress high-channel-count connections into a single cable by pairing tunnel endpoints. One input-side tunnel connects to the signal source; the matching endpoint outputs the tunneled channels at the destination. Each pair consumes one channel on the cable it travels through but carries up to 32 channels inside the tunnel. Better P2P's Advanced Memory Card simplifies tunnel pairing by storing endpoint link data, replacing the tedious right-click-to-pair workflow when managing many tunnels across a large base."]
