		{
			dependencies: ["AE01000000000012"]
			description: ["Wireless Crafting Terminals connect to the network via a Wireless Access Point placed on any cable segment; they require charge and range. The AE2 Wireless Terminals mod also provides the Wireless Universal Terminal, which combines terminal, pattern encoding, and extended functionality into one handheld device. The AE Infinity Booster card extends wireless range significantly when inserted into a terminal — build one as soon as the wireless terminal becomes your primary interface, since default range is limited to a small radius around the access point."]
