		{
			dependencies: ["AE01000000000021"]
			description: ["GTCEu ME Input and Output Buses replace the traditional export-bus-to-chest-to-input-hatch pipeline with a direct network-to-machine connection. The ME Input Bus pulls items from the network into the machine's processing slot; the ME Output Bus pushes results directly back into the network. ME Input and Output Hatches do the same for fluids. These eliminate the intermediate chest layer entirely and make GTCEu machine automation significantly cleaner. The GT machine and the AE2 network must share a power source — connect them through compatible cable interfaces."]
