			description: ["The GTCEu ME Assembler is a tiered GT machine that performs AE2 crafting-type recipes at GT machine speed with overclocking support. Higher tiers run faster. Connect via Pattern Provider with the relevant crafting patterns loaded; results return to the network through the output bus. The GTCEu Large ME Assembler is a multiblock version with higher base throughput. Use GT ME Assemblers for high-volume crafting operations that overwhelm standard Molecular Assembler arrays — the speed difference at IV tier and above is substantial."]
