		{
			dependencies: [
				"AE01000000000017"
				"AE01000000000009"
			]
			description: ["The Storage Bus exposes an adjacent non-AE2 inventory — chest, barrel, or machine buffer — as a virtual storage location on the network. Items in the external inventory become searchable and withdrawable through ME Terminals as if they were inside a Drive. Use Storage Buses to integrate high-capacity vanilla storage (barrels for bulk materials) without converting to ME cells. Always configure the bus filter to restrict which item types it indexes — an unfiltered Storage Bus on a crowded machine buffer increases terminal search time and can mask inventory state."]
			id: "AE01000000000027"
