		{
			dependencies: ["AE01000000000011"]
			description: ["MEGACells extends the cell component tier above 256k with components at 1M, 4M, 16M, 64M, and 256M bytes. Each tier follows the same housing and component assembly workflow as standard cells but requires higher-tier materials. Mega cells are essential for endgame bulk storage — a single 256M cell holds more material than a full Drive of 256k cells. MEGACells also provides the Bulk Cell, which stores a single item type in unlimited quantity at the cost of only tracking that one type. Build bulk cells for materials that genuinely overflow standard mega cells."]
			id: "AE01000000000028"
