		{
			dependencies: ["AE01000000000012"]
			description: ["The ME Requester (from ME Requester mod) places automated crafting requests to the AE2 network on a configurable schedule. Set a target stock level for any craftable item; the Requester submits a crafting job whenever network stock drops below that threshold. This turns autocrafting from a reactive system into a proactive one — items are produced in advance rather than on demand. The Requester Terminal provides a network-wide view of all active requesters and their stock levels. Use requesters for materials that are consumed continuously and must never go to zero."]
