		{
			dependencies: ["AE01000000000009"]
			description: ["The AE2 Network Analyser (from AE2 Network Analyser mod) is a handheld diagnostic tool that displays channel usage, power draw, and component counts for any network segment you right-click. It removes the guesswork from channel debugging — when a component drops offline unexpectedly, the analyser shows exactly which cable segment hit saturation and which component claims what channel budget. Keep one in your inventory when expanding the network; debugging a channel overflow without it requires tracing every cable run manually."]
