		{
			dependencies: ["AE01000000000016"]
			description: ["The Programmed Circuit Card (from PC Card mod) is a pattern-configurable circuit card that replicates the GTCEu circuit selector mechanic inside the AE2 autocrafting system. When encoded into a pattern, it specifies which GTCEu circuit configuration the machine should use for that recipe — solving the ambiguity that arises when a single machine has multiple recipes that differ only by circuit number. Without it, the network cannot distinguish between circuit 1 and circuit 2 variants of the same recipe. Configure one card per circuit variant required by your autocrafting setup."]
